{"tid":2258563,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"33萬食衛局長WhatsApp戶被盜　料誤信騙徒交驗證碼或誤入木馬連結","createTime":"2020-10-26T06:40:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T07:40:55.000Z","uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b3d6658347e192347060974d5afb0653e9138ebb","tid":2258563,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:40:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201026/P6WQJFI34RDBVNCMGLNQSNRIPI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201026%2FP6WQJFI34RDBVNCMGLNQSNRIPI%2F&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oK0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=daf5db52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201026%2FP6WQJFI34RDBVNCMGLNQSNRIPI%2F&h=66a0943a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201026/P6WQJFI34RDBVNCMGLNQSNRIPI/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FT7GV45QVZGZLGJQBQXYVW24FM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFT7GV45QVZGZLGJQBQXYVW24FM.png&h=3da87a4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食物及衞生局回覆傳媒查詢時證實，局長陳肇始一個WhatsApp賬戶早前曾被他人盜用短暫未能使用。<br />\n<br />\n月薪$335,100的食物及衞生局局長陳肇始，其一個WhatsApp賬戶早前被他人盜用，當局回覆傳媒時指，未有政府工作相關資料外洩。<br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局昨日（25日）回覆傳媒查詢時證實，局長陳肇始一個WhatsApp賬戶早前曾被他人盜用短暫未能使用，經資訊科技組人員跟進及檢查後，至今未有發現與政府工作相關資料外洩。<br />\n<br />\n食衞局已通報資科辦及政府資訊保安事故應變辦事處，但未有交代賬戶何時被盜用等資料 。<br />\n<br />\n資訊科技商會榮譽會長方保僑指，現時WhatsApp一般建議需要開啟兩步驗證碼，但駭客可能假扮WhatsApp團隊，要求用戶提供相關驗證碼，最終用戶被偷去控制權。另外亦可能是陳局長收到外來連結，打開後電話被木馬程式入侵，終被盜去賬戶。<br />\n<br />\n方又指，現時發送SMS驗證碼方式存在漏洞，「網上可以撈到」，有德國銀行用戶亦曾試過被偷去兩步驗證碼。"},{"pid":"bfc3d7afefb491e4a943ec6a56097b9f15ae7762","tid":2258563,"uid":55597,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:42:04.000Z","msg":"政府 d 宣信片，公務員自己都唔睇"},{"pid":"8d8bc62d7f30e94995f613a830627cd7e4c0f54f","tid":2258563,"uid":55597,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:42:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>政府 d 宣傳片，公務員自己都唔睇</blockquote>"},{"pid":"97b30b3029a79248ea6e5b9ffe9871d420046879","tid":2258563,"uid":309357,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:43:04.000Z","msg":"早前我都試過<br />\n<br />\n原因：衰戇鳩，但33萬局長同我一樣咁戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b845bf55193610a4b228fb2e20e82a229c4abf4d","tid":2258563,"uid":275525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T07:09:14.000Z","msg":"SMS verify code 都偷到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係佢自己硬膠膠比左個code 人"},{"pid":"d4f8d72a5b7d94df8e0363e807fe28edd0c33ff6","tid":2258563,"uid":203431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T07:25:22.000Z","msg":"經資訊科技組人員跟進及檢查後，至今未有發現與政府工作相關資料外洩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪檢查咗騙徒部手機有冇cap圖"},{"pid":"36158bd4fbaf66e73f539e781b2c198b8f6abcd0","tid":2258563,"uid":192052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"97b30b3029a79248ea6e5b9ffe9871d420046879","tid":2258563,"uid":309357,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:43:04.000Z","msg":"早前我都試過<br />\n<br />\n原因：衰戇鳩，但33萬局長同我一樣咁戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T07:40:55.000Z","msg":"正面啲 香港高官入職要求低<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}